author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of L7 featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2018.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 One More Thing
00:03:55 Pretend We’re Dead
00:07:21 Dispatch from Mar-a-Lago

Musicians
Donita Sparks — vocals, guitar
Jennifer Finch — bass
Suzi Gardner — guitar, vocals
Demetra Plakas — drums

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.

author: The Current
description:
Brigitte Calls Me Baby performing "Too Easy" at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube 

"We Were Never Alive" is from Brigitte Calls Me Baby’s 2024 album, The Future Is Our Way Out, available on @atorecords . Brigitte Calls Me Baby are set to headline The Current's 21st Anniversary Celebration at First Avenue on Friday, Jan. 23, 2026. Find more information at thecurrent.org/anniversary.
